&lt;h2>Architecture&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="architecture">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#architecture" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Monorepo with two packages:&lt;/p>
